{"tid":1154429,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實廣東話係咪已經無得救？","createTime":"2019-05-14T09:51:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T10:09:34.000Z","uid":49836,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"23ed7fe8928ecc6a08a28c15a1bf77cf9a068780","tid":1154429,"uid":49836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:51:09.000Z","msg":"以前落黎香港住既大陸人 大多都好願意學講廣東話 願意融入香港社會 但近年發現好多新黎既大陸人 都唔會學講廣東話 直接用普通話同人溝通 尤其係小學生 係街見到好多新移民既小學生都係用一口流利既普通話溝通 <br />\n<br />\n而識一啲係廣州住既朋友都話我知 而家好多新一代既'廣州人'都已經唔識講廣東話 因為父母係由其他省市搬黎廣州 而學校亦都強制學生講普通話 <br />\n<br />\n其實廣東話真係好好聽 大家好好珍惜仲有廣東話聽既日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講到呢到有啲感慨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申家母都係十幾年前跟我爸落黎香港 但好努力學廣東話 好肯講 講左十幾年 雖然都係有啲口音 但至少願意講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7c70b83aa9b25493d74f6da4cca1d06743a4cc","tid":1154429,"uid":49836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:51:41.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43172d209eb316cef51c389d0e8ea393117668b4","tid":1154429,"uid":49836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"466aeb6a22e1af0e0d2a7fe865d24131a3e71f21","tid":1154429,"uid":49836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:52:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d216fe7f1e58c4d463f4bd6d35a9c96087ab98","tid":1154429,"uid":49836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb286